e thirty pieces of silver and threw it into the house of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", to the potter. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"One Hb ms, Syr read treasury"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:15","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:3–10","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 26:15","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 27:3–10","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Syr reads treasury"},{"marker":2,"text":"One Hb ms, Syr read treasury"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:11:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then I cut in two my second staff, Union, annulling the brotherhood between Judah and Israel."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:11:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" also said to me, “Take the equipment of a foolish shepherd. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:11:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am about to raise up a shepherd in the land who will not care for those who are perishing, and he will not seek the lost "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or young"},{"kind":"text","text":" or heal the broken. He will not sustain the healthy, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or exhausted"},{"kind":"text","text":" but he will devour the flesh of the fat sheep "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:3–4","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and tear off their hooves."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 34:3–4","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or young"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or exhausted"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Zec:11:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Woe to the worthless shepherd"},{"kind":"text","text